  "detailed_description": "<strong>GUILTY</strong> is a first-person psychological horror game.<br><br><strong>STORYLINE</strong><br>Play as <i>Peter</i>, an ex-military, and discover what your past hides. Access your unconscious to remember the traumatic and most terrifying memories that are hidden. Find out what happened to <i>Linda</i>, Peter's wife. A traumatic past that gives you a sense of guilt. What would you do if past trauma no longer allowed you to have a normal life?<br><br><br><strong>GAMEPLAY</strong><br><br>With just the help of a flashlight, explore a national park and a terrifying house inside your mind to relive your traumas and face them. Solve puzzles to gain access to important areas. Explore, remember, run and survive. Try to overcome your fears.<br><br>Collect memory fragments to access your unconscious.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2129720/extras/7aa9a5cae79e4fe5c2747885a9d6f057.poster.avif?t=1663282293\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2129720/extras/7aa9a5cae79e4fe5c2747885a9d6f057.webm?t=1663282293\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2129720/extras/7aa9a5cae79e4fe5c2747885a9d6f057.mp4?t=1663282293\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Explore caves where a dark ritual is taking place.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2129720/extras/bb495d426c6777386babe0db5d8e3af9.poster.avif?t=1663282293\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2129720/extras/bb495d426c6777386babe0db5d8e3af9.webm?t=1663282293\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2129720/extras/bb495d426c6777386babe0db5d8e3af9.mp4?t=1663282293\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Find out what's real and what's hallucination.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2129720/extras/75f6e7a6422a64f540619a48743d6de9.poster.avif?t=1663282293\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2129720/extras/75f6e7a6422a64f540619a48743d6de9.webm?t=1663282293\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2129720/extras/75f6e7a6422a64f540619a48743d6de9.mp4?t=1663282293\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Be tormented by darkness.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2129720/extras/cb218133d6a48e71a10eb15ed5ac2d4d.poster.avif?t=1663282293\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2129720/extras/cb218133d6a48e71a10eb15ed5ac2d4d.webm?t=1663282293\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2129720/extras/cb218133d6a48e71a10eb15ed5ac2d4d.mp4?t=1663282293\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Explore the house to find levers that unlock access to restricted areas.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2129720/extras/73a890d906fa67c3c05c4c08b7552cfd.poster.avif?t=1663282293\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2129720/extras/73a890d906fa67c3c05c4c08b7552cfd.webm?t=1663282293\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2129720/extras/73a890d906fa67c3c05c4c08b7552cfd.mp4?t=1663282293\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Discover the correct way to position the mannequins to progress in the game.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2129720/extras/4fc747d879e34819a309ee944b91aa91.poster.avif?t=1663282293\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2129720/extras/4fc747d879e34819a309ee944b91aa91.webm?t=1663282293\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2129720/extras/4fc747d879e34819a309ee944b91aa91.mp4?t=1663282293\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The answers you find facing your fears!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2129720/extras/7681cd0d9fb2f065bcc715bfe07efed3.poster.avif?t=1663282293\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2129720/extras/7681cd0d9fb2f065bcc715bfe07efed3.webm?t=1663282293\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2129720/extras/7681cd0d9fb2f065bcc715bfe07efed3.mp4?t=1663282293\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
